This ticket template is for bug/error reports. 
If you are suggesting a feature and not reporting a bug please delete all the text here and begin your ticket Title with SUGGESTION:

What steps will reproduce the problem?
What is the expected output?
What is your TownyEco version? (Do not say "latest".)

What is your spigot/craftbukkit version? (Do not say "latest".)
